{"tid":2090334,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"支那：再次強調沒有任何一個示威者因香港公安而死亡","createTime":"2020-07-02T06:06:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T13:41:13.000Z","uid":21470,"like":3,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"14187fd18ced553ff185454fa90c1232591e1a7f","tid":2090334,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T06:06:07.000Z","msg":"外交部反駁西方 強調港區國安法不損港人自由<br />\n02.07.2020 13:55<br />\n<br />\n外交部就一些美國及西方人士就香港、新型冠狀病毒疫情及新疆等問題，指責中國人權狀況，作出37項反駁，其中10項涉及香港。外交部強調， 港區國安法只是針對分裂國家、顛覆國家政權、恐怖活動及勾結外國或境外勢力危害國家安全等4類犯罪行為，港人享有的言論、新聞、集會、遊行及示威等權利和自由都會獲得保障，世界上100多個國家的憲法都規定，行使基本權利和自由不得危害國家安全，在港區國安法實施後，將更有利於在港企業履行尊重人權的責任。<br />\n<br />\n外交部又強調，香港警隊在反修例示威中展現克制，極為專業，沒有一位示威者因警隊執法而死亡，截至5月底，卻有超過590名警務人員在執法中受傷。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1326812&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1326812%26csid%3D261_341&d=oBn6KkEvnt0QU92xe9ZG8DMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=d734ad09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1326812&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"a4983708e6de81dde0d8f421d124b59f2245a819","tid":2090334,"uid":2300,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T06:06:26.000Z","msg":"64無死人"},{"pid":"bdeaa49317c5dbf899b700410e952e14f233daba","tid":2090334,"uid":205927,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T06:06:31.000Z","msg":"64有冇人死？"},{"pid":"bbcfe0e54d7bc24099ca9d5fb64d52d87d79a0c4","tid":2090334,"uid":26385,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T06:07:03.000Z","msg":"即係有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71ce086932ef33f9fdff7545888efa85ec1c17a5","tid":2090334,"uid":2419,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T06:07:23.000Z","msg":"周梓樂？"},{"pid":"713e78717fbb88781a01826f3527e993a2d833a6","tid":2090334,"uid":3440